When upgrading from 0.5.6 to 0.5.8:
 1) Replace the following files with updated versions:
	/var/www/html/php/siteheader.php
	/var/www/html/php/user_auth.php
	/var/www/html/php/w3table_paged.php
	/var/www/html/php/templates/* (all files get updated!!!)
	/var/www/html/error_doc/*.html

 2) Rename /var/www/html/php/config.php to /var/www/html/php/w3config.php

 3) Add the following new files:
	/var/www/html/ui/local/w3php-banner.jpg

 4) Change use of global variables $w3bodyjs and $bead_crumbs

When upgrading from 0.5.4 to 0.5.6:

 1) Replace the following files with updated versions:
	/var/www/html/php/siteheader.php
	/var/www/html/php/QuickForm/Renderer/w3v8.php
	/var/www/html/php/w3table.php
	/var/www/html/php/w3table_paged.php
	/var/www/html/php/templates/* (all files get updated!!!)
	/var/www/html/error_doc/401.html
	/var/www/html/error_doc/403.html
	/var/www/html/error_doc/404.html

 2) Add the following new files:
	/var/www/html/ui/local/valid-xhtml10.png

 3) Delete the following files:
	/var/www/html/ui/css/table2.css

 4) Edit /var/www/html/php/config.php and verify the following settings exist:
    xhtml_valid.

When upgrading from 0.5.2 to 0.5.4:

 1) Replace the following files with updated versions:
	/var/www/html/php/siteheader.php
	/var/www/html/php/user_auth.php
	/var/www/html/php/ldap.php
	/var/www/html/php/w3table.php
	/var/www/html/php/templates/* (all files get updated!!!)
	/var/www/ui/css/table2.css

 2) Add the following new files:
	/var/www/html/php/w3form.php
	/var/www/html/php/w3table_paged.php
	/var/www/html/QuickForm
